	(text "IR GATE TRUTH TABLE:\nbeam PRESENT -> phototransistor ON  -> SIGx ~0V  -> comparator OUT LOW\nbeam BROKEN  -> phototransistor OFF -> SIGx ~5V  -> comparator OUT HIGH\nGATEx HIGH = marble in beam. Firmware timestamps the RISING edge.\n(open-collector outputs pulled to 3V3: Pico-safe levels)"
